        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Jay Miller\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n Jay Miller:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>When you say you opened the Amiot Servelle 5 hours before serving do you mean you pulled the cork or that you decanted?</p>\n<p>I\u2019m always looking for signs of hope that 1995s are coming around <img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/images/emoji/unicode/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Pulled the cork.  I never decant red burgundy.</p>",
